  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:0",
      "text": "Overview（概述）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:1",
      "text": "此模式实际会 bake integrator 的 outputs。它主要用于 bake diffuse global illumination，但也可以 bake 任意 light path expression。",
      "ascii_letters": 73,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:2",
      "text": "How does it work?（它如何工作？）",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:3",
      "text": "Scene objects 场景对象会逐个 baked。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:4",
      "text": "integrator 会在每个 point 上以 single increment 运行（Max Samples = 1）。",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:5",
      "text": "结果会 output 到一个或多个 AOVs，每个 AOV 只包含一个 display channel。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:7",
      "text": "illumination baking settings 只会 override 你的 scene render globals 中的一部分 parameters。如果当前 scene 的 render 符合预期，那么这些就是 bake 所需的全部 settings。",
      "ascii_letters": 85,
      "cjk_chars": 29
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:8",
      "text": "Bake Mode（烘焙模式）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:9",
      "text": "此 menu 的主要用途是在 rendering 前 validate 你的 setup，并在检测到 incorrect setup 时发出 warning。",
      "ascii_letters": 47,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:11",
      "text": "为每个 object 生成 1 张 image。",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:12",
      "text": "所有 baked objects 都必须具有用于 baking 的 valid uvs 有效 UVs",
      "ascii_letters": 29,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:13",
      "text": "3D Point Cloud（3D 点云）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:14",
      "text": "根据 file naming format，生成一个或多个 point clouds。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:15",
      "text": "在 world space 中 bake",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:16",
      "text": "Baking Image File Format（烘焙图像文件格式）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:17",
      "text": "通常，你会用 tokens 创建一个 pattern 来生成 named AOVs，但这里有一点不同。默认 file pattern 为：",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:18",
      "text": "是一个 new attribute，可在 Attribute Editor 的 RenderMan section 中所有 bake-able shapes 上找到：",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:21",
      "text": "如果想 bake 到单个 3D point cloud，应从 file name pattern 中移除",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:23",
      "text": "Bake to Maps (2D baking)（烘焙到贴图，2D 烘焙）",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:24",
      "text": "选择 global baking resolution。更大的 resolutions 会需要更长 render 时间。",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:25",
      "text": "Limitation（限制说明事项）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:26",
      "text": "所有 objects 都会以相同 resolution baked。这是当前 implementation 的 limitation。",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:27",
      "text": "Bake to Point Cloud (3D baking)（烘焙到点云，3D 烘焙）",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:28",
      "text": "Point clouds 会在 world space 中 baked，其 density 取决于 shape 的 dicing density。在此为 scene 选择 global dicing density。",
      "ascii_letters": 75,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:29",
      "text": "你可以通过将 Dicing Strategy 设置为 worlddistance 并输入不同的 Dicing Distance Length，按 shape override dicing density。较小 values 会创建更多 points。",
      "ascii_letters": 85,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:30",
      "text": "Integrator（积分器）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:31",
      "text": "选择一个 integrator 及其 settings。我们推荐 PxrPathTracer。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:32",
      "text": "Limitation（限制说明事项）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:33",
      "text": "某些 integrators（如 PxrVCM 和 PxrUnified）",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:34",
      "text": "incompatible 不兼容状态",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:35",
      "text": "，因为它们完全依赖 incremental rendering 来 accumulate samples，并随时间 resolve illumination。",
      "ascii_letters": 56,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:36",
      "text": "Baking 会运行 integrator",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:39",
      "text": "在 single increment 中提供良好结果",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:41",
      "text": "为获得最佳结果，需要充分增加 direct samples（light samples 和 BXDFs samples）以及 indirect samples 的数量，以得到 reasonably clean results。最佳 settings 高度依赖 scene，需要通过 experimentation 确定。",
      "ascii_letters": 102,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:42",
      "text": "Limitation（限制说明事项）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:45",
      "text": "（即 brute-force），因此无论 convergence 如何，都会计算所有 samples。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:46",
      "text": "Illumination baking 可能非常慢：请确保你",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:48",
      "text": "，并记住 baked illumination 中少量 noise 几乎不可见。",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:49",
      "text": "请注意，bake view-dependent illumination（如 specular）没有意义；应始终尽量 bake diffuse、albedo 等 view-independent signals。",
      "ascii_letters": 76,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:50",
      "text": "Limitation（限制说明事项）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:51",
      "text": "目前无法在 baked 2D images 上运行 denoiser。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:52",
      "text": "Default Ray Depth（默认射线深度）",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:53",
      "text": "照常可以设置 max diffuse depth 和 specular depth。这会在 baking 期间 override 常规 scene settings。",
      "ascii_letters": 55,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:55",
      "text": "AOV section 的工作方式与 render globals 中完全相同。",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:56",
      "text": "默认情况下，我们会 bake diffuse illumination，包括 direct 和 indirect。",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:57",
      "text": "如果需要 bake raw illumination，还需要同时 bake albedo，并将 illumination 除以 albedo（在 compositing package 或 shader 中），以获得 raw illumination（也称为 irradiance）。",
      "ascii_letters": 96,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:58",
      "text": "Limitation（限制说明事项）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:59",
      "text": "每个 AOV（也称为 Display）只能包含一个 display channel，最多 output 4 个 channels（RGBA）。",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:60",
      "text": "添加更多 displays 可 bake 更多 channels。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:62",
      "text": "任何 non-deep image format 都可用于 bake 到 images。推荐使用 OpenEXR，以避免 clamped results。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:65",
      "text": "display driver 显示驱动来 bake point clouds。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:66",
      "text": "如果忘记这样做，preflight checks 应会 warning 并 cancel bake render。",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:67",
      "text": "Launching a bake render（启动 bake render 渲染任务）",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:68",
      "text": "bake render 本质上是一个只有一项 setting 不同的 batch render。它使用 bake Hider，而不是 raytrace Hider。",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:69",
      "text": "要启动 bake render，只需选择",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:70",
      "text": "Bake Render: Illumination",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:71",
      "text": "，而不是 RenderMan menu 中的 Batch Render。所有常规",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:72",
      "text": "batch render preferences 批量渲染首选项",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "464a7b0d32:73",
      "text": "都会应用到 bake render。",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    }
  ],
